Scry on Familiar										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality			VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The master may scry on his familiar (as if casting the scrying spell) once per day.
Speak One Language									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:A raven familiar can speak one language of its master's choice as a supernatural ability.
